{"tid":1902681,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（單車）環阿聯酋賽因武漢肺炎取消","createTime":"2020-02-28T13:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T14:42:44.000Z","uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"781f9fcff0da16e42e6352b94a81dd35827e3924","tid":1902681,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"暫時得英文新聞，但好大件事<br />\n<br />\n消息指UAE車隊2名意大利籍工作人員被驗出對武漢肺炎呈陽性反應<br />\n<br />\n環阿聯酋賽即時取消最後2站（之前已完成5站， Adam Yates總排名領先），所有車隊車手同工作人員都需要檢驗同留酒店隔離<br />\n<br />\n今屆參賽車手有Froome, Valverde, Cavendish等名將，亦有Groenewegen, Ewan, Bennett, Ackermann等衝刺好手<br />\n<br />\n如果真係出現大爆發既話班大牌車手都幾危下&hellip;"},{"pid":"b15d0888c47c0ba7b4d4ef1ad05de77ed5b313c3","tid":1902681,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"另外因為單車賽既歐洲古典賽期就快開始，意大利既疫情已經令唔少賽事有可能要取消，包括5大古典賽事之一既Milano San Remo<br />\n<br />\n而疫情向歐洲各國擴散之下受影響既比賽可能會更多&hellip;"},{"pid":"b38e6d73f7922155b28dc08a9485e64bfc60568e","tid":1902681,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/final-uae-tour-stages-called-off-over-coronavirus-fears/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cyclingnews.com%2Fnews%2Ffinal-uae-tour-stages-called-off-over-coronavirus-fears%2F&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=36207361\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/final-uae-tour-stages-called-off-over-coronavirus-fears/</a>"},{"pid":"fa62c1ccdfe2395a4b9c050d7f0d0362e87273ca","tid":1902681,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UW61Fqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUW61Fqs.jpg&h=c6bc113b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b239fd8436036e8729922f0ee50bbfbd9f72ef9","tid":1902681,"uid":63331,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:56:10.000